---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Privacy Policy | Open Energy Services" 
  description="Privacy policy for Open Energy Services. Learn how we protect and handle your data."
>
  <div class="pt-32 pb-24 bg-white min-h-[60vh]">
    <div class="container max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-navy mb-8 tracking-tight">
        Privacy Policy
      </h1>
      <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none text-slate-600 font-medium">
        <p class="mb-4">Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-GB')}</p>
        <p class="mb-4">
          At Open Energy Services, we are committed to protecting and respecting your privacy. This policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when you use our website and services.
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-navy mt-8 mb-4">1. Information we collect</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We collect information that you provide to us directly, such as your name, email address, phone number, and property details when you complete an eligibility check or contact form.</p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-navy mt-8 mb-4">2. How we use your information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">We use your information to assess your eligibility for government funding, to match you with accredited installation partners, and to communicate with you about your energy efficiency options.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-navy mt-8 mb-4">3. Sharing your information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">To provide our matching service, we may share your details with carefully selected, fully vetted installation partners. We will never sell your data to third parties for marketing purposes.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-primary-navy mt-8 mb-4">4. Contact us</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">If you have any questions about this privacy policy or how we handle your data, please contact us at welcome@openenergyservices.co.uk.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>